Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:56.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:58.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:01.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:13.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:18.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:23.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:28.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:32.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.47,0:01:36.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:39.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:43.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:48.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:05.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:06.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
